snippet.title: Obama in the Dark (Inkagames) - Walkthrough
snippet.description:
Hi everyone! Obama in the Dark is one of my favorite sagas, it has three parts and a fourth is coming, so I hope I can bring them all before its release 😅 Good Luck!
● Description: Obama goes on a dangerous mission to investigate the strange events that are occurring in an abandoned mansion.
● Play it here: http://www.inkagames.com/flash_games/obama_in_the_dark.html
● Want to subscribe?  ( ͡° ͜ʖ ͡°) : https://www.youtube.com/c/escapegameplays?sub_confirmation=1
